body:
### My Repos
* [node-red-contrib-blindcontroller](https://github.com/alisdairjsmyth/node-red-contrib-blindcontroller) - Node-RED node that determines blind position based on the position of the sun and climatic conditions
* [node-red-contrib-sunpos](https://github.com/alisdairjsmyth/node-red-contrib-sunpos) - Node-RED node that emits the position of the sun
* [node-red-contrib-qmotion](https://github.com/alisdairjsmyth/node-red-contrib-qmotion) - Node-RED node to control QMotion blinds using a QSync device
* [node-red-contrib-lifx-api](https://github.com/alisdairjsmyth/node-red-contrib-lifx-api) - Collection of Node-RED nodes to control LIFX globes using the HTTP Remote Control API
